Join the Conversation To find out more about Facebook commenting please read the Conversation Guidelines and FAQs Sunday Sports Talk breaks down Vols comeback Nick Carboni 11:57 a.m. EDT October 11, 2015 CONNECT TWEET LINKEDIN COMMENT EMAIL MORE 
The Sunday Sports Talk Crew breaks down Tennessee's 21-point comeback to beat No. 19 Georgia. 
It tied the program's third-biggest comeback, and gave the Vols their first win over a Top 25 opponent since 2013. Sunday Sports Talk breaks down Vols comeback WBIR 
CAK's Josh Smith scored a touchdown to spark the comeback. CAKs Josh Smith and running back Alvin Kamara spark comeback WBIR 
The Vols improve to 3-3 (1-2 SEC). They are off on Oct. 17, and play at Alabama on Oct. 24. 
Sunday Sports Talk airs every Sunday after Tennessee football games at 10 a.m., on WBIR. Read or Share this story: http://on.wbir.com/1RB8c3p TOP VIDEOS
